divs: Sighting Details Standing on the back porch and looking up at the sky, when 6 to 10 orange colored object flew over the North side of Clarion Pa. In a eastenly direction at high speed. There was no sound and no one around to verify the sighting. The formation was not a tight v shape but loose,as the objects flew away the formation completely stay close but not in v formation, but refomed into v shape
